33
00:04:23,929 --> 00:04:26,348
What about you, huh?

34
00:04:26,432 --> 00:04:29,935
There's... There's not much to tell.

35
00:04:31,603 --> 00:04:34,440
<i>I was on my way home from work, and...</i>

36
00:04:34,523 --> 00:04:36,567
I don't remember anything else.

37
00:04:41,405 --> 00:04:43,407
First dead body I've ever seen.

38
00:04:44,533 --> 00:04:46,243
<i>They look different in real life.</i>

39
00:04:48,370 --> 00:04:50,414
They don't move.

40
00:04:55,127 --> 00:04:58,047
From the looks of these chains,

41
