or you'd be dead by now.

48
00:05:19,151 --> 00:05:20,527
Trust me.

49
00:05:20,611 --> 00:05:22,654
<i>-What are you, a surgeon?
-Yeah.</i>

50
00:05:26,074 --> 00:05:27,075
So...

51
00:05:28,619 --> 00:05:31,205
Are you gonna tell me
