52
00:05:34,666 --> 00:05:36,710
Adam.

53
00:05:37,878 --> 00:05:39,922
Well, Adam...

54
00:05:41,256 --> 00:05:43,801
What we need to do...

55
00:05:43,884 --> 00:05:46,220
